[woman] An imposter
with no medical training

94
00:04:40,346 --> 00:04:42,680
posed as a surgeon and bungled
a minor operation

95
00:04:42,681 --> 00:04:44,482
to remove a child's tonsils.

96
00:04:44,483 --> 00:04:47,552
The patient recovered fully
after additional treatment.

97
00:04:47,553 --> 00:04:51,422
1 is six months on probation,
7 is ten years in prison.

98
00:04:51,423 --> 00:04:53,358
[Sheldon]
Okay.

99
00:04:53,359 --> 00:04:56,728
If you are taking on the persona
of a doctor,

100
00:04:56,729 --> 00:05:02,967
we would expect good behavior.

101
00:05:02,968 --> 00:05:04,736
[woman] The surgeon botched
the operation

102
00:05:04,737 --> 00:05:06,871
