the influence of narcotics,

103
00:05:06,872 --> 00:05:08,906
causing her to have permanent
hoarseness

104
00:05:08,907 --> 00:05:14,712
and ruining her career.

105
00:05:14,713 --> 00:05:16,748
A 16-year-old girl who had just
received her license

106
00:05:16,749 --> 00:05:18,116
drove through a red light,

107
00:05:18,117 --> 00:05:19,817
hitting another car
that was being driven

108
00:05:19,818 --> 00:05:25,723
by a talented pianist.

109
00:05:25,724 --> 00:05:27,792
A couple was taking their two
children to the playground

110
00:05:27,793 --> 00:05:29,927
when they saw a woman
sunbathing nude.

111
00:05:29,928 --> 00:05:32,430
Look at that.
There could be a gender gap.

112
00:05:32,431 --> 00:05:34,866
We're also learning a lot about
the worldviews people have.

113
00:05:34,867 --> 00:05:40,872
[Jeff]
Yeah, absolutely.

