118
00:05:48,781 --> 00:05:50,848
Wow, she went 1
right away.

119
00:05:50,849 --> 00:05:53,618
She's not a fan of authority
and rules.

120
00:05:53,619 --> 00:05:58,956
[Sheldon]
Yeah.

121
00:05:58,957 --> 00:06:01,492
Okay, thank you so much
for your time.

122
00:06:01,493 --> 00:06:02,693
We really appreciate it.

