 For example...

139
00:06:50,709 --> 00:06:54,011
 The point is to prime
 their mortality salience.

140
00:06:54,012 --> 00:06:56,013
 Let's see if this group
 is more punitive

141
00:06:56,014 --> 00:06:59,650
 towards worldview
 violations.

