a fundraising manager
fled with all the money

145
00:07:06,725 --> 00:07:08,993
and was arrested months later
in Tasmania.

146
00:07:08,994 --> 00:07:11,062
1: three months in prison;

147
00:07:11,063 --> 00:07:13,164
7: ten years in prison.

148
00:07:13,165 --> 00:07:17,568
Please answer now.

149
