236
00:11:19,211 --> 00:11:20,811
The right thing
by their own worldview,

237
00:11:20,812 --> 00:11:22,513
but by the same token,
when we think about death,

238
00:11:22,514 --> 00:11:24,115
we want to do what's right.

239
00:11:24,116 --> 00:11:26,383
And if we're acting
like jurors,

240
00:11:26,384 --> 00:11:28,352
we want to make
the right decisions.

241
00:11:28,353 --> 00:11:30,287
As we very much learned today,

242
00:11:30,288 --> 00:11:34,024
