one thing one way or the other.

243
00:11:34,025 --> 00:11:35,893
It's just to reduce
uncertainty...

244
00:11:35,894 --> 00:11:38,195
-That's correct.
-...in the most careful way.

245
00:11:38,196 --> 00:11:42,333
Absolutely. To know a little bit
more today than yesterday.

246
00:11:42,334 --> 00:11:46,804
[Jeff]
Yeah.

247
00:11:46,805 --> 00:11:48,172
[Michael]
Our pilot test shows

248
00:11:48,173 --> 00:11:50,007
that there's still a lot
to discover

249
00:11:50,008 --> 00:11:51,408
about terror management

