615
00:28:01,879 --> 00:28:03,847
Because I just figured

616
00:28:03,848 --> 00:28:05,215
I'll figure that out
when I'm older.

617
00:28:05,216 --> 00:28:07,183
-But I could die at any time.
-You sure could.

618
00:28:07,184 --> 00:28:09,285
So I want to be prepared.

619
00:28:09,286 --> 00:28:11,221
And I want my wishes
to be known.

620
00:28:11,222 --> 00:28:13,490
-Yeah.
-So I have decided

621
00:28:13,491 --> 00:28:15,158
when that moment comes,

622
00:28:15,159 --> 00:28:19,262
I want it to be my final moment
of existence.

623
00:28:19,263 --> 00:28:22,832
I want to give all my atoms and
molecules back to the universe.

624
00:28:22,833 --> 00:28:25,802
And I've decided that
I want to die.

625
00:28:25,803 --> 00:28:27,904
Oh, I'm so glad
you've made that decision.

626
00:28:27,905 --> 00:28:29,172
And you've come
to the right place.

627
00:28:29,173 --> 00:28:33,143
I want to be naturally buried.

628
00:28:33,144 --> 00:28:34,811
I want to have a green burial.

629
00:28:34,812 --> 00:28:37,881
You know, become worm food
