00:28:37,882 --> 00:28:39,449
I want it all
to go back to earth.

631
00:28:39,450 --> 00:28:43,319
But I kind of want a place
where people can come

632
00:28:43,320 --> 00:28:46,923
to be like,
that's where he was buried.

633
00:28:46,924 --> 00:28:52,095
So there's everything from
just little discs in the ground

634
00:28:52,096 --> 00:28:54,497
where you are,
